TY  - JOUR
TI  - A Monte Carlo Study of Estimates of Simultaneous Linear Structural Equations
AU  - Wagner, Harvey M.
AB  - [A Monte Carlo sampling technique is employed to compare small sample properties of limited-information--single-equation, least squares, and instrumental variables estimates. Two versions of an essentially two equation model are each used to generate 100 sets of observations over 20 time periods.]
